title: American Horror Story Freak Show - Main Title
author: American Horror Story Brasil
comment: Achei incrível! Uma bela mistura de aberrações retratadas de uma forma bizarra e clássica. Uma obra de arte. Essa forma de animação é espetacular.
Is this official? Because it's absolutely amazing!!
Don't take me wrong, I'm not saying I don't like it (I LOVE AHS) but this intro didn't creep me out at all
I finished the entire season in one sitting, it was just so good. The opening was un-skippable for me
